{
  "title": "GUI-LHADDAS",
  "description": "<p>GUI-LHADDAS is a cross-platform desktop application providing a graphical user interface for LHADDAS, a system that integrates the local-scale high-resolution atmospheric dispersion model LOHDIM-LES and the dose evaluation code SIBYL. It integrates input preparation, simulation execution, and interactive 3D geospatial visualization (via CesiumJS) of atmospheric dispersion and gamma-ray dose-rate results in a single workflow.</p>",
